### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3001/api

### Set this after creating a category
@categoryId = YOUR_CATEGORY_ID_HERE

### ============================================
### GET ALL PRODUCTS (No authentication needed - Public endpoint)
### ============================================

### 1. Get All Products (Default)
GET {{baseUrl}}/products

### 2. Get Products with Pagination
GET {{baseUrl}}/products?page=1&per_page=8

### 3. Get Products - Page 2
GET {{baseUrl}}/products?page=2&per_page=5

### 4. Filter by Category
GET {{baseUrl}}/products?category={{categoryId}}

### 5. Filter by Price Range
GET {{baseUrl}}/products?min_price=10&max_price=50

### 6. Filter by Type (Organic)
GET {{baseUrl}}/products?type=Organic

### 7. Filter In-Stock Only
GET {{baseUrl}}/products?in_stock=true

### 8. Text Search
GET {{baseUrl}}/products?search=quinoa

### 9. Sort by Price Ascending
GET {{baseUrl}}/products?sort_by=price_asc

### 10. Sort by Price Descending
GET {{baseUrl}}/products?sort_by=price_desc

### 11. Sort by Name A-Z
GET {{baseUrl}}/products?sort_by=name_asc

### 12. Sort by Name Z-A
GET {{baseUrl}}/products?sort_by=name_desc

### 13. Sort by Newest
GET {{baseUrl}}/products?sort_by=newest

### 14. Sort by Rating
GET {{baseUrl}}/products?sort_by=rating

### 15. Combined Filters - Complex Query
GET {{baseUrl}}/products?category={{categoryId}}&min_price=20&max_price=100&type=Organic&in_stock=true&sort_by=price_asc&page=1&per_page=10

### 16. Search + Filter + Sort
GET {{baseUrl}}/products?search=organic&type=Organic&sort_by=rating&per_page=5
